{"word":"G5461 - φωτίζω - phōtízō - fo-tid'-zo - Enlighten","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φωτίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phōtízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fo-tid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Enlighten</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெளிச்சம் கொடு, பிரகாசி, வெளியரங்கமாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to give light, to shine"},{"paragraph":"2. to enlighten, light up, illumine"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5457 - φῶς - phōs - foce/5457\">G5457</a>; to <i>shed rays</i>, that is, to <i>shine</i> or (transitively) to <i>brighten</i> up (literally or figuratively): - enlighten, illuminate, (bring to, give) light, make to see.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2017/2017\">G2017</a>, <a href=\"#/G2020/2020\">G2020</a>, <a href=\"#/G5457/5457\">G5457</a>, <a href=\"#/G5458/5458\">G5458</a>, <a href=\"#/G5459/5459\">G5459</a>, <a href=\"#/G5460/5460\">G5460</a>, <a href=\"#/G5461/5461\">G5461</a>, <a href=\"#/G5462/5462\">G5462</a>"}]}